                 <table>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                    These parameters yield the circular sequence {-5, -5, 7, 5, 0, 8, 1, 0, 6, 0, 1, 7, -10, -5, 5, 5, 5, 5}. The maximum value is achieved by taking all elements except -10 and -5 at the near end.
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
                </td>
               </tr>
              </table>
